videos.description: Ole Miss strikes first against LSU with a 15-yard TD made possible by a 50-yard gain.
videos.headline: Ole Miss seizes chance for TD

videos.description: Leonard Fournette shows off that he's back from injury, going 59 yards untouched in a flash to cut LSU's deficit to 10-7 against Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Fournette is back with a vengeance and a 59-yard TD

videos.description: Leonard Fournette delivers a crushing blow to an Ole miss safety on a 22-yard gain.
videos.headline: Fournette bulldozes Ole Miss defender

videos.description: D.J. Chark run for a loss of 16 yards to the LSU 35 D.J. Chark fumbled, forced by Victor Evans, recovered by Miss Marquis Haynes  , return for 7 yds to the LSU 35
videos.headline: Ole Miss blows up jet sweep to force fumble

videos.description: Chad Kelly pass intercepted Donte Jackson return for no gain to the LSU 2
videos.headline: Ole Miss gives ball right back to LSU with interception

videos.description: LSU's D.J. Chark walks in a 40-yard TD to pull out in front of the Rebels 13-10.
videos.headline: LSU capitalizes on momentum with effortless TD

videos.description: Leonard Fournette is giving the college football world a reminder that he's back with his second long touchdown run of the game, this time from 76 yards out to increase the LSU lead.
videos.headline: Fournette does it again, busts loose for 76-yard TD

videos.description: Danny Etling sacked by Marquis Haynes for a loss of 7 yards to the LSU 9 Danny Etling fumbled, recovered by Miss
videos.headline: LSU fumble sets up Ole Miss in red zone

videos.description: Ole Miss converts an LSU turnover into a touchdown when Akeem Judd punches it in from two yards out. The Rebels would then get the two-point conversion to make it 21-21 at the half.
videos.headline: Ole Miss ties the game with TD just before halftime

videos.description: C. Kelly Run For Two-point Conversion
videos.headline: Ole Miss ties game with two-point conversion

videos.description: Already with a pair of long touchdowns in the game, Leonard Fournette does it again, this time from 78 yards out to give LSU the lead again at 28-21.
videos.headline: Fournette won't be stopped, goes 78 yards for another TD

videos.description: Chad Kelly pass intercepted Duke Riley return for 3 yds to the Miss 25
videos.headline: C. Kelly pass intercepted by D. Riley

videos.description: Danny Etling pass intercepted Derrick Jones return for 2 yds to the Miss 16
videos.headline: D. Etling pass intercepted by D. Jones

videos.description: LSU RB Leonard Fournette makes his comeback game a memorable one with three touchdown runs in a win over Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Fournette makes a big statement

videos.description: Leonard Fournette shares what his mindset was when he ran over a defender and his thoughts on his big night against Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Fournette would rather give a hit than take a hit

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Fournette would rather give a hit than take a hit) 2016/10/22 SC

videos.description: Leonard Fournette breaks LSU's single-game rushing record on just his first eight carries and the No. 25 Tigers beat No. 23 Ole Miss 38-21.
videos.headline: Tigers top Rebels 38-21

videos.description: After missing LSU's last three games with a broken left ankle, Leonard Fournette plays his best game of the season breaking LSU's single-game rushing record with 284 rushing yards and three scores against Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Fournette makes a record-breaking statement in his return

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Fournette makes a record-breaking statement in his return) 2016/10/22 ESHEET ENHL
